1.100.0 (2026-07-15)
	First release. Upstream Tailscale v1.100.0 cross-compiled for
	plan9/amd64 with stock Go 1.26 — no patches, upstream supports
	GOOS=plan9 since 2025. Userspace WireGuard (gVisor netstack), so it
	runs on a stock 9front kernel.

	Ships /amd64/bin/tailscale (CLI), /sys/lib/tailscale/tailscaled
	(daemon) and /rc/bin/tailscaled, a wrapper that configures the
	loopback interface tailscaled's control socket needs (fresh 9front
	has no 127.0.0.1) and defaults --statedir to $home/lib/tailscale.

	Verified on bare-metal 9front (cirno): daemon brings up the
	WireGuard engine, reaches controlplane.tailscale.com over TLS,
	registers a node key and issues a login URL; `tailscale status` /
	`tailscale up` work against it.
